{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@interface","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNMapSnapshotter","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSObject","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSObject"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/StaticSnapshotExample"]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can change the snapshotter’s options at any time and reuse the snapshotter","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"for multiple distinct snapshots; however, the snapshotter can only generate one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"snapshot at a time. If you need to generate multiple snapshots concurrently,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"create multiple snapshotter objects.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For an interactive map, use the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},{"text":" class. Both ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},{"text":" are compatible with offline packs managed by the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"},{"text":" class.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"From a snapshot, you can obtain an image and convert geographic coordina